faq.title: Frequently Asked Questions About Our AI Image Generator
faq.description: Have questions about our AI image generator? Contact us on Discord or by email.

items.title: What is an AI image generator and how does it work?
items.description: An AI image generator uses advanced machine learning models (like GPT-4o) to create AI images from text descriptions. Our AI image generator interprets your words to generate unique AI-generated images matching your vision. Simply describe what you want, and our AI image generator creates stunning AI images instantly.

items.title: Can I use the AI-generated images commercially?
items.description: Yes! All AI images you generate with our AI image generator have full commercial usage rights. You can use your AI-generated images in projects, products, marketing materials, or anywhere else without restrictions.

items.title: What AI image styles are available in your AI image generator?
items.description: Our AI image generator supports dozens of AI image styles including anime, photorealistic, 3D render, oil painting, watercolor, sketch, pixel art, and many more. You can also mix AI image styles or create custom AI-generated image variations to match your exact needs.

items.title: How long does it take to generate AI images?
items.description: Most AI images are generated in 5-15 seconds depending on complexity and resolution. Our AI image generator processes batch AI image generations in parallel, so creating multiple AI images doesn't take significantly longer.

items.title: What AI image resolution can I get from your AI image generator?
items.description: You can generate AI images up to 4K resolution (4096x4096 pixels) with our AI image generator, perfect for printing, high-quality displays, and professional use. Standard AI image generations start at 1024x1024 pixels.

items.title: Do I need design skills to use this AI image generator?
items.description: Not at all! Our AI image generator is designed to be intuitive for everyone. Just describe what AI images you want in plain English, and our AI image generator handles the rest. The more detailed your description, the better the AI-generated images, but you can start simple with our AI image generator.
